text: Lina Lehtovaara (born 23 June 1981) is a Finnnish international football referee. She has been an international football since 2009. Lehtovaara was a referee at the UEFA Women's Euro 2022 in England. ==References== Category:Finnish footballers Category:Sportswomen Category:Living people Category:1981 births Category:Association football referees
